Definition: the quality of being current or of the present
Example: a shopping mall would instill a spirit of modernity into this village
Synonyms: adj, all, progressive, modern, nonclassical, fashionable, modernness, late, modernism, modernistic, contemporaneity, contemporaneousness, synchronous, contemporaneous, currency, the, quality, of, being, current, or, present, a, shopping, mall, would, instill, spirit, into, this, village
Category: noun.attribute
